  "Ashok Kajaria is the chairman and managing director of listed Kajaria Ceramics, which was founded by him in 1988.",
  "The company is India's largest manufacturer of ceramic tiles, which it manufactures in eight factories across the country.",
  "Both his sons Chetan and Rishi help him run the company as joint managing directors.",
  "Bollywood actor Akshay Kumar is Kajaria's brand ambassador."
